                    </choice> mehr bloß dem <placeName type="place" key="Lukmanier (Pass)">Lucmanier</placeName>, sondern demjeni<lb break="no" xml:id="p4-l13"/>g<supplied>en</supplied>
                    <placeName type="place" key="Alpen">Alpen</placeName>bahnprojecte zu Theil werd<supplied>en</supplied> soll<supplied>en</supplied>, welches die mei<lb break="no" xml:id="p4-l14"/>sten Aussicht<supplied>en</supplied>
